<h3><a href="http://www.dnr.state.ga.us/lpb/">Land Protection
Branch</a></h3>
<p><a href="http://www.dnr.state.ga.us/lpb/SWACT95.pdf">Georgia
Comprehensive Solid Waste Management Act Of 1990</a><br>
<a href="http://www.dnr.state.ga.us/lpb/SMRULES.pdf">Rules
Chapter 391-3-3 Amended Surface Mining</a><br>
