<h3><a href="http://167.193.53.2/EPD/apb/index.htm">Air
Protection Branch</a></h3>
<p>The Georgia Air Branch has provided all Georgia Air Quality
applications in electronic format. This file (<a
href="http://167.193.53.2/EPD/apb/titlev.exe">TITLEV.EXE</a>)
specifically contains all documentation required to complete and
submit a Georgia Title V application. This file also contains the
latest version of the Georgia Rules, SIP application, Synthetic
Minor application and the Permit-by-Rule application. <br>
(Only the Title V application can be submitted in electronic
form. All other applications must be submitted as a hard copy to
the Georgia Air Branch.)<br>
</p>
<h3><a href="http://167.193.53.2/EPD/wpb/index.htm">Water
Protection Branch</a></h3>
