<DOCHDR>
http://www.dnr.state.ga.us:80/EPD/pr122096.htm 167.193.53.2 19970121095253 text/html 5514
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 09:56:47 GMT
